                <p class="lead">Custom development for law firm systems—document management integrations, practice management extensions, client portals, and workflow automation.</p>

                <p>Law firms run on specialized software. I build the custom pieces that connect your systems, automate manual workflows, and give attorneys the tools they actually need. Whether it's integrating with iManage, extending your practice management system, or building a client-facing portal, I deliver code that works reliably in demanding legal environments.</p>

                <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3">What I Build for Firms:</h4>
                <ul class="mb-4">
                    <li><strong>DMS Integrations:</strong> Custom integrations with iManage, NetDocuments, and other document management systems</li>
                    <li><strong>Practice Management Extensions:</strong> Extending Aderant, Elite, or custom time and billing systems</li>
                    <li><strong>Client Portals:</strong> Secure matter status, document sharing, and collaboration platforms</li>
                    <li><strong>Workflow Automation:</strong> Intake forms, approval processes, and document assembly</li>
                    <li><strong>E-Discovery Tools:</strong> Custom processing, review, and production workflows</li>
                </ul>

                <p>I understand the security, compliance, and reliability requirements that legal technology demands. More on <a href="/services/custom-software-development">custom software development</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

