                <p class="lead">Senior technical leadership without the overhead of a full-time hire. I work with your IT team to drive technology initiatives forward.</p>

                <p>Big Law has enterprise-scale complexity but often without enterprise-scale IT departments. I bring twenty years of experience leading technical teams to firms that need senior leadership for specific initiatives—whether that's a DMS migration, a new client portal, or modernizing legacy systems.</p>

                <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3">How I Help Law Firm IT Teams:</h4>
                <ul class="mb-4">
                    <li><strong>Technical Leadership:</strong> Architecture decisions, vendor evaluation, implementation strategy</li>
                    <li><strong>Project Management:</strong> Keeping complex initiatives on track</li>
                    <li><strong>Team Augmentation:</strong> Additional senior capacity when you need it</li>
                    <li><strong>Vendor Coordination:</strong> Working with your technology vendors to get results</li>
                    <li><strong>Knowledge Transfer:</strong> Building your team's capabilities as we work together</li>
                </ul>

                <p>I integrate seamlessly with existing teams and processes. No ego, no disruption—just results.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

